    public interface ComputerStaticStateDataI
extends fr.upmc.components.interfaces.DataOfferedI, fr.upmc.components.interfaces.DataRequiredI
    The interface ComputerStaticStateDataI defines the static state notification services for Computer components.

    Description

    The interface extends the standard DataOfferedI and DataRequiredI with their methods to pull and push data.
